snippet.title: Kirby: Canvas Curse ᴴᴰ Full Playthrough
snippet.description:
This is our true HD (1440p 60fps) full playthrough of Kirby: Canvas Curse for the Nintendo DS showing off the game from start to finish. A 100% walkthrough is currently being worked on

Character: Kirby
Mode: Main Story
Text Language: English

Kirby: Canvas Curse for Nintendo DS
Published by Nintendo
Developed by HAL Laboratory
Released on June 13, 2005

Nintendo Utopia provides the highest quality no commentary gameplay on YouTube.
